95
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,680
I'll handle that.

96
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:18,880
I'll go with you.

97
00:06:29,020 --> 00:06:36,020
(Xinggang Hospital)

98
00:06:43,270 --> 00:06:44,310
