125
00:08:03,950 --> 00:08:04,790
Hey, Zhizhou.

126
00:08:05,390 --> 00:08:06,230
You don't come here.

127
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:07,360
Go back to Xingchen

128
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:09,270
