206
00:14:20,270 --> 00:14:21,110
Thanks.

207
00:14:21,240 --> 00:14:22,080
You're welcome.

208
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:26,150
Such a gentleman.

209
00:14:27,670 --> 00:14:28,600
Xing!

210
00:14:28,910 --> 00:14:30,600
