Miss Li, what do we do?

299
00:19:52,750 --> 00:19:53,590
Xing,

300
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:55,160
what do we do now?

301
00:19:55,880 --> 00:19:56,750
How about I go downstairs

302
00:19:56,750 --> 00:19:57,750
and talk to them?

303
